/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T00:43:52.000Z","msg":"對港共施政無影響<br />\n所以我完全無感覺<br />\n<br />\n​即係反送中前線打生打死，又警暴又制度暴力呢樣果樣<br />\n香港人奇望美國做既，就係要令到某幾個高官一下還曬按揭<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得今次美國既「加強制裁」「無用」，就係咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果要達到一個「合理對等既效果」，根本完全唔撚夠強<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我已經唔係要港共政府等價交換啦<br />\n<br />\n你可以話係「岩岩開始陸續有黎」既<br />\n不過我真係唔會期望太多"},{"pid":"1f7959cb226e90791018094d861978b14c9b7362","tid":2449964,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8917a0b3a55a8cb6215ddf44febd896dfcc6bb6f","tid":2449964,"uid":248522,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"9d5ae6f08d04e66029ae99204cd392e257d0a0c2","tid":2449964,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T05:07:22.000Z","msg":"換湯不換藥<br />\n一啲實感都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T00:32:32.000Z","msg":"有用過樓樓主開post討論"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T00:46:12.000Z","msg":"唔留你，你可以去返格黎PO了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n傳送門：<br />\n(有圖)最新24位被制裁官員名單<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2450103\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2450103</a>"},{"pid":"00cc25db3082cb679c54f8adf1508005f5101fec","tid":2449964,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f7bc3f67d6e9b3d787f052e8910fa1a8a8542a4","tid":2449964,"uid":88743,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10b1eadbbd6ab73b9ebcbee2b6a716be3c6da952","tid":2449964,"uid":151074,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T00:31:24.000Z","msg":"無感覺就唔洗一下還曬按揭啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T00:43:52.000Z","msg":"對港共施政無影響<br />\n所以我完全無感覺<b